ture partners=E2=80=94but <em>mainly</em> lawyers=E2=80=94incorporating Puc=
k and formally beginning the extensive legal process that would lead to our=
 Series A investment.=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:
0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">I=E2=80=99m not th=
e sedentary type, and I=E2=80=99m surely not the pandemic type, and by Janu=
ary of 2021, I can assure you that I was driving my family <em>apoplectic</=
