n Zooms and Google Meets pitching a novel subscription-focused media compan=
y focused on the inside conversation, built on a model that enshrined talen=
t
with equity and bonuses befitting their exemplary influence. And by the win=
ter, understandably, they=E2=80=99d had enough. So instead of rolling calls=
 from my home office in our old attic, I took my work on the road. I=E2=80=
=99d layer up and walk to the local tennis courts, pacing around for hours =
while I took legal notes and chatted into my ear buds, always cognizant of =
what I was paying out of pocket per hour.</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bo=
ttom:0px;">=C2=A0</p><p style=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">I don=E2=80=
